        excerpt: "Working with electronics, batteries, and power tools requires proper safety knowledge. Learn essential safety practices to protect yourself and your equipment.",
        lastUpdated: "2026-03-28",
        author: "SafeSolder"
      },
    ],
  },
  "enclosures": {
    name: "Enclosures",
    description: "Find the perfect housing for your cyberdeck. From rugged Pelican cases to custom 3D printed designs, explore enclosure options for every skill level and budget.",
    articles: [
      {
        slug: "pelican-case-builds",
        title: "Pelican Case Cyberdecks",
        excerpt: "Pelican cases provide excellent protection and a blank canvas for creative builds. Learn how to modify these rugged cases for electronics.",
        lastUpdated: "2026-04-12",
        author: "HardCaseHero"
      },
      {
        slug: "3d-printed-enclosures",
        title: "3D Printed Enclosure Design",
        excerpt: "Design and print your own custom enclosure. This guide covers CAD software options, print settings, and finishing techniques.",
        lastUpdated: "2026-04-09",
        author: "PrintMaster"
      },
      {
        slug: "upcycled-enclosures",
