        excerpt: "For desktop-class performance in a portable form factor, Intel NUC systems offer x86 compatibility and powerful integrated graphics.",
        lastUpdated: "2026-04-04",
        author: "X86Fan"
      },
    ],
  },
  "displays": {
    name: "Displays",
    description: "Screen technologies for cyberdecks including e-ink for low power, vibrant LCDs and OLEDs, and creative solutions like round displays.",
    articles: [
      {
        slug: "e-ink-displays",
        title: "E-Ink Display Integration",
        excerpt: "E-ink screens offer incredible battery life and a unique aesthetic. Learn about controller boards and software setup for e-ink displays.",
        lastUpdated: "2026-04-10",
        author: "InkMaster"
      },
      {
        slug: "lcd-vs-oled",
        title: "LCD vs OLED for Cyberdecks",
        excerpt: "Compare display technologies including brightness, contrast, power consumption, and durability for portable cyberdeck applications.",
        lastUpdated: "2026-04-06",
        author: "ScreenGuru"
      },
    ],
  },
